title: hitting the ground running in nyc

description:
DANIELLE IS OFFICIALLY MOVED AND SETTLED IN NYC!  Join the gals from Brooke’s apartment as they get into what the past week has been like.  The gals talk about their wild weekend on the town, Danielle’s moving struggles and what life in the city is like.  The gals ALSO announce that they are HIRING!  See below for the link. Good luck! Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening stories + screenshots on Instagram.
